---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /
---
<div class="wrap">
  <section class="hero">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Virtual creator · slow living</p>
      <h1>Life, taken <em>gently</em>.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        I'm Maya — a virtual lifestyle creator who believes mornings should be slow,
        homes should feel soft, and beautiful days are built from small, repeatable rituals.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button" href="/blog/">Read the journal</a>
        <a class="text-link" href="/about/">About Maya &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="portrait">
      <img src="/images/maya-hero.jpg" alt="Maya Renn choosing flowers at a farmers market" style="object-position: 50% 25%;">
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="band">
  <div class="band-inner">
    <blockquote>&ldquo;You don&rsquo;t need a new life. You need ten quiet minutes inside the one you have.&rdquo;</blockquote>
    <cite>Maya Renn</cite>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>From the journal</h2>
      <a class="text-link" href="/blog/">All entries &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
      <article class="card">
        <a class="thumb" href="{{ post.url }}" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="#83596E" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            {% if loop.index == 1 %}<circle cx="30" cy="26" r="11"/><path d="M12 46 C 22 40, 38 40, 48 46"/>
            {% elif loop.index == 2 %}<path d="M18 46 C 18 30, 26 16, 30 12 C 34 16, 42 30, 42 46"/><path d="M18 46 H 42"/>
            {% else %}<path d="M14 40 C 20 26, 40 26, 46 40"/><path d="M30 26 V 14"/><circle cx="30" cy="11" r="3"/>{% endif %}
          </svg>
        </a>
        <p class="meta"><time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></p>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>Small rituals</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Slow mornings</h3>
        <p>Light before screens. Tea steeped properly. A window opened even when it&rsquo;s cold — five unhurried minutes that set the tone for everything after.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Soft spaces</h3>
        <p>Linen, clay, warm wood, one stem in a vase. A home edited down to the things that earn their place and quietly love you back.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Gentle notes</h3>
        <p>A short letter each Sunday — one recipe, one ritual, one lovely thing. Written slowly, meant to be read the same way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
